    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It runs like a total dream and is ready for your next big road trip. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, you\u2019ve found it! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
