      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade FD3S RX-7, showcasing the pinnacle of 13B-REW sequential turbocharging. This example maintains perfect compression across all rotor faces, with the complex 'rat's nest' vacuum system recently refreshed to factory specification. The chassis remains incredibly rigid, featuring untouched double-wishbone geometry and a Torsen limited-slip differential that ensures linear power delivery. Every engagement of the short-throw five-speed manual is tactile and crisp, while the cooling system has been meticulously overhauled to preserve the thermal integrity of the apex seals. A rare find for the purist seeking uncompromised, factory-spec rotary performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
