      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute showroom-quality specimen, meticulously preserved to satisfy the most discerning collector. The exterior features a flawless, deep-gloss finish entirely free of swirls, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent, with the premium leather upholstery remaining supple and devoid of any bolster wear or creasing. Every electronic feature and mechanical system functions with precision, reflecting a life spent in climate-controlled storage and a rigorous adherence to preventative maintenance. Accompanied by a complete service dossier, this car represents a rare opportunity to acquire a legendary model in its most pristine, untouched state.",
