      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she's a total dream. This car is in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered in a garage its whole life and has been driven so gently. If you're looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the dealership headache, you've found it. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy this beauty as much as I have!",
